Intentionality and Agency
  In communicating and manipulating Wintermute says its forced to deal with _givens_, takes adv of what already exists. Wintermute manipulates characters thru some formative emotional exp that they've had or some significant relationship (especially considering how he not only gets them to work for him but managed to move them around)

At the hear of the book...
  to what extent are we in control of our actions and to what extent are our actions determined by forces outside of our control?


