  Identity
    there are countless igredients that make up the human body and mind, like all the components that make up me as an individual with my own personality. Sure I have a face and voice to distinguish myself from others, but my thoughts and memories are unique only to me, and i carry a sense of my own destiny. each of those things are just a small part of it. i collect information to use in my own way. all of that blends to create a mixture tht forms me and gives rise to my conscience.
      -kusanagi

