how is sex treated? how is sexuality treated?
  commoditized
  an object, bought, sold
  angel is able to use it as a weapon, get what she needs

  what's the significance of the scne with the "cowboy"? (note the play here, we have a real cowboy and not a cyber-cowboy). What does it mean that he is gay?

