    in the story it's actually something you hook up to your biology

    def of cyborgs, natural progression of the body into alternate versions of intercourse

  "I believe that organic sex, body against body, skin against skin is becoming no longer possible. what we're getting is a whole new order of sexual fantasies, involving a different order of experiences like car crashes, like travelling in jet planes, the whole overly of new technologies, architecture, interior design, communications, transport, merchandizing, etc"

  Does 2nd life > real life?

  in learning about machine sex we see two of the chars become addicted to angel's program. is this addiciton similar to the addiction ppl experience to 2nd life or WoW?
  
