what is the nature of knowledge at the end of f451
  define your terms
    knowledge in the framework, etc etc

    traditionally knowledge is viewed as a static sort of entity, i.e. contained, here we have knowledge being changed from an object, knowledge is embodied and by doing this we can argue that knowledge becomes less stable, 

    is neuromancer a thought experiment
      is not because it is more concerned with the aesthetics of the world than the premise or extrapolation

